~~~~~ AUTONOMOUS MODE INFORMATION ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

** Auto modes can be switched in the BASIC tab (first box) on the dashboard.**
** Ensure that an auto mode is set to prevent crashing **

Current available modes:

0 - IDLE
1 - FORWARD; drives forward for the time indicated in the code
2 - ZIG-ZAG; zig-zags, each motion happens for the time indicated in the code
3 - SPIN; spins for the time indicated in the code
9 - SELF TEST; activates all mechanisms sequentially to check for issues